headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Scope Out the Pfister Growler, Vapid Dominator GTT, and Dinka RT3000 on the Test Track
content: If you’re in the market for a new top-of-the-line car, you might want to pay the LS Car Meet’s Test Track a visit: this week, you can put the Pfister Growler, Vapid Dominator GTT, and Dinka RT3000 through their paces, either by whipping around on the painted track, Time Trials, or a friendly competitive Scramble.
